summary: This is an internal FBI email forwarding a victim contact list for the Epstein case, discussing victim notification and support coordination between cases. It includes a confidentiality notice regarding the handling of sensitive information.
keyFacts: An FBI email from July 26, 2019, forwards a victim contact list for the Epstein case.
The email discusses coordinating victim notification and support between multiple cases.
The document contains a confidentiality notice warning against unauthorized disclosure of Personally Identifiable Information (PII).
The email references both current and former cases involving Epstein victims.
